productReviews.reviewText: My co-worker Luka has one of these. He says it looks purple.
The box this comes in is 5 kilometer by 6 meter and weights 20 ounce!
one of my hobbies is mushroom cultivation. and when i'm cultivating mushrooms this works great.
I saw one of these in Canada and I bought one.
i use it profusely when i'm in my garage.
